{"tid":1100089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那工人沒錢上賓館　住古墓睡朱元璋女兒棺木","createTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T09:25:36.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"293dede28e577552dfb9e3b6d72651dcf1f3bfef","tid":1100089,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"中國南京有一群農民工，平時以打零工維生，身上沒有太多錢，連住個便宜賓館都變成經濟負擔。這些工人居無定所，有無多餘金錢租屋的狀況之下，乾脆變成「古墓派」，住進朱元璋女兒「福清公主」的墓穴中，睡在福清公主的棺木上。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《網易》報導，這個古墓具有600多年歷史，是朱元璋第8個女兒福清公主的墓室，古墓裡陰暗潮濕，但這裡反而成為窮困工人的臨時庇護所，曾經最多住過20~30人，至今仍可看到棺木上和墓穴裡，到處都有棉被、櫥櫃等生活雜務。<br />\n<br />\n工人們說，他們平時打零工，沒有固定收入，連下一份工作在哪裡都不知道，「哪有那個錢天天上賓館」。還有工人說：「我們窮到連鬼都不怕了！」這讓福清公主的古墓，反倒成為工人們最可靠、免錢的住所，加上這裡也靠近市中心，對於工人們來說，真的是最佳的住宿地點。<br />\n<br />\n不過這種「住古墓」的現象，一直都讓政府當局相當頭痛，尤其在保護文物這一塊，長期無法徹底執行。2016年，政府當局曾經做過一次「大清理」，讓這些農工搬走，並送上免費大衣和棉被，也聯繫過一些廉價賓館，讓農工們免費住宿，但一些人始終持保持抗拒態度，官員們就說：「你來他走，你走了他又來了。」這幾年許多農工又陸續成為「古墓派」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qw3wLQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqw3wLQx.jpg&h=cfed078d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGLCGoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGLCGoT.jpg&h=ca527ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKD45Qy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKD45Qy.jpg&h=6f4e9559&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8efbe39d7154471a82f6e20c675e6a0863d1bbc","tid":1100089,"uid":29080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"真正古墓派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545b9f7f697d75756ea295f221591f27ea9014bb","tid":1100089,"uid":40101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"果然窮鬼先係最惡"},{"pid":"c9a51827606865e6280a454e334367244336ae4e","tid":1100089,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"545b9f7f697d75756ea295f221591f27ea9014bb","tid":1100089,"uid":40101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"果然窮鬼先係最惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:16:35.000Z","msg":"一係就死，都無咩所謂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d21a6aae0e521838257c11ce207ada0dc730e4","tid":1100089,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f392982b59b2ee120410a8c54367064c5971945","tid":1100089,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1d21a6aae0e521838257c11ce207ada0dc730e4","tid":1100089,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7b/Biskupin_012_women_skeleton.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F7%2F7b%2FBiskupin_012_women_skeleton.jpg&h=bd5db3d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a19c1b74a5a7720b7a5a897d5d8692efc3877c8","tid":1100089,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"一個公主晚晚畀唔同人訓過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e36051dfad543fe9830aaf039bcd65afbe7109","tid":1100089,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a19c1b74a5a7720b7a5a897d5d8692efc3877c8","tid":1100089,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"一個公主晚晚畀唔同人訓過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31b869c9a373f7adb423477833178c2a0b4b470","tid":1100089,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q